configuration.models.custom.description:
Configure custom language models for each provider. These models will be used instead of retrieving the model listing from the provider.

**Note:** This setting does not affect GitHub Copilot models.

**Example**:
```json
{
  "anthropic": [
    {
      "name": "Claude Sonnet 4.5",
      "identifier": "claude-sonnet-4-5",
      "maxInputTokens": 200000,
      "maxOutputTokens": 8192
    }
  ],
  "openai-compatible": [
    {
      "name": "Custom Model",
      "identifier": "custom-model-id"
    }
  ]
}
```
